---
// What You Actually Need Component
---

<div class="bg-white py-16">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Headline -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-4">
      What You Actually Need
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 text-center mb-12">
      (Not Everything They Sell)
    </p>

    <!-- Opening -->
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 text-center mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Both insurers will try to sell you 5-7 products. <span class="font-semibold">Most expats need 2-3.</span>
    </p>

    <!-- Two Column Layout - What You Need / Understanding Products -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-12">
      
      <!-- Left Column - Typical Setup -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Typical Setup:</h3>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-200 mb-6">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-600 mr-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Basic insurance (HMO model)</span>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">CHF 326/mo</span>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-green-600 mr-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Outpatient supplementary</span>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-900 font-semibold">CHF 158/mo</span>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-gray-400 mr-3" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                  <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
                  <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"></line>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Optional: Dental</span>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-600 font-semibold">CHF 65/mo</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Total:</span>
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600">CHF 484-549/mo</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">for comprehensive coverage</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What You DON'T Need -->
        <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-red-200">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What You DON'T Need:</h4>
          
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
              </svg>
              <p class="text-gray-700"><span class="font-bold">Completa Extra</span> - Absolutely NOT advised! Duplicate coverage with Completa/Optima</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
              </svg>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Multiple hospital plans (pick ONE if you want private rooms)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
              </svg>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Travel insurance (unless you're abroad 2+ months/year)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column - Understanding Products -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Understanding the Products:</h3>
        
        <!-- Helsana Products -->
        <div class="mb-8">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center">
            <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-gray-600 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
            Helsana Supplementary
          </h4>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Completa</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Basic outpatient: Alternative medicine, prevention, CHF 200 gym coverage/year</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Top</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Enhanced outpatient: Higher limits for alternative medicine, wellness, dental contributions</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Primeo</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Premium outpatient: Maximum coverage for all supplementary services, highest dental limits</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Swica Products -->
        <div class="mb-8">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center">
            <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-red-600 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
            Swica Supplementary
          </h4>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <div class="bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Optima</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Best value: Alternative medicine, CHF 1,300 gym coverage/year, prevention, glasses</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Completa Top</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Enhanced outpatient: Higher limits than Optima, more alternative therapy coverage</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Completa Forte</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Balanced option: Mid-level coverage between Optima and Completa Top</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Supplementa</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Hospital insurance: Private/semi-private room, worldwide coverage options</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Key Benefit Callout -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 rounded-lg p-6 text-white">
          <p class="font-bold mb-2">Why This Matters:</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-red-100">Swica's CHF 1,300 gym coverage vs Helsana's CHF 200 = <span class="font-bold text-white">CHF 1,100 difference/year</span>. This alone can cover your entire supplementary premium!</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Insider Note -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md border-l-4 border-red-600">
      <div class="flex items-start">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
          <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
          <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"></line>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold mb-2">Insider Truth</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">We've saved clients <span class="font-bold text-red-600">CHF 300-500/month</span> by cutting unnecessary products. We get paid the same commission either way - we recommend what you actually need.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Subtle CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <button 
        onclick="window.openHealthModal('consultation')"
        class="text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 font-medium underline text-lg"
      >
        Want a personalized product recommendation? â†’ Book consultation
      </button>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

